{"tid":2121621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場新聞: 大角咀海輝道公園大量船員自出自入","createTime":"2020-07-23T12:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T14:05:35.000Z","uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0c320fe4015ef9b2edb005adddc12ba024d23250","tid":2121621,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:05:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3290865384332392/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3290865384332392%2F&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=e6f021be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3290865384332392/</a><br />\n<br />\nStand News 立場新聞<br />\n25m &middot;<br />\n<br />\n香港本月爆發第三波肺炎疫情，多宗確診個案與獲豁免檢疫的船員有關。《立場新聞》今午（23日）到大角咀海輝路海濱公園，留意到有兩艘接駁船到碼頭，首批接戴約 30 名船員上船離港，另一批接戴十多名船員抵港。其中一名等候離港的船員表示，正等候病毒檢測結果，已被告知不能到處走，故從早上開始已在海濱公園流連多個小時。記者觀察所見，有不少沒有戴口罩的跑步人士、居民及外傭、野餐家庭在船員旁邊經過。<br />\n<br />\n負責接送船員的船代理向《立場新聞》表示，由於香港豁免下船換班的船員檢疫，吸引不少船隻到港停泊及換班，生意較過往上升 2 至 3 倍，但他直言，寧願政府加強船員入境限制，也不想發「死人財」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/109518446_3290864304332500_1362728604986257695_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=1C9FzOQnI-UAX--9bYR&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=0eec9514b0bf63d57de4d9aa905360cd&amp;oe=5F3DBB4A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F109518446_3290864304332500_1362728604986257695_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3D1C9FzOQnI-UAX--9bYR%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3D0eec9514b0bf63d57de4d9aa905360cd%26oe%3D5F3DBB4A&h=e50bd4aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/109747173_3290864254332505_2382955043889908919_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=Ch1qVpCsOuwAX8KwAYs&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=f249db339e27a4c15641321602d78573&amp;oe=5F401FB2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F109747173_3290864254332505_2382955043889908919_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DCh1qVpCsOuwAX8KwAYs%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3Df249db339e27a4c15641321602d78573%26oe%3D5F401FB2&h=82f6e50f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/110113411_3290864467665817_3920861713433890678_o.png?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=4cYo1S0TndsAX-NzZDX&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=7c959169b6b1bb5f60f807b8d85208d5&amp;oe=5F3DF5E2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F110113411_3290864467665817_3920861713433890678_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3D4cYo1S0TndsAX-NzZDX%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D7c959169b6b1bb5f60f807b8d85208d5%26oe%3D5F3DF5E2&h=42ed7ff4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b695b4f86b6639a6529fca73193899d8f6c134a3","tid":2121621,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:06:34.000Z","msg":"推，好大個漏洞"},{"pid":"28e0ead951bff78cec2ef68aa0a02d3b0a4b92e2","tid":2121621,"uid":12267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:07:09.000Z","msg":"推😡😡😡😡"},{"pid":"fed3668c1da3f9efbf66b54aa979c9cac40197f5","tid":2121621,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:24:43.000Z","msg":"再推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f680ec372af1d2a3a44c932f48128a4957193fc","tid":2121621,"uid":263223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:29:45.000Z","msg":"屌喇星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />附近啲屋苑真係多撚謝"},{"pid":"b4c3b3e5347c4a715e96d77daa2a8a7d00c82140","tid":2121621,"uid":288913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:05:35.000Z","msg":"內河船碼頭成日都有中國船員上落，佢哋雖然同入境處嘢或者海事處有登記，但係好多時落咗船都會周圍走。<br />\n<br />\n利伸：以前係佢哋間公司（主要營運商）嘅商業夥伴"}]}